snippet.title: [UK] Something legendary is happening in Pokémon UNITE!
snippet.description:
Suicune dashes into the fray on March 1st!

Plus look forward to Alolan Raichu and Alcremie both joining the Pokémon UNITE roster in 2025.

Remoat Stadium will also be returning to ranked matches for a limited time to celebrate Pokémon Day alongside a new type of battle called First to 500!
